    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>44564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_003_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はぁん？　誰に向かってタンス言ってんだど！
おめぇなんぞ、毛も生えてねぇ、ハゲぼうずのくせが！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Who are you calling a wardrobe?! You’re just a bald little brat with no hair!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>25</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46292</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_003_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ほら、ふたりともけんかしちゃだめ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey, you two, no fighting!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
